IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. PROCESS-CLAIM.
AUTHOR. HEALTHINSURE CORE TEAM.

ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-POLICY-ACTIVE       PIC X(1).
01 WS-COVERAGE-REMAINING  PIC 9(12).
01 WS-CLAIM-AMOUNT        PIC 9(12).
01 WS-DAYS-ACTIVE         PIC 9(5).
01 WS-OUTPUT              PIC X(200).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY 1 UPON ARGUMENT-NUMBER.
    ACCEPT WS-POLICY-ACTIVE FROM ARGUMENT-VALUE.
    DISPLAY 2 UPON ARGUMENT-NUMBER.
    ACCEPT WS-COVERAGE-REMAINING FROM ARGUMENT-VALUE.
    DISPLAY 3 UPON ARGUMENT-NUMBER.
    ACCEPT WS-CLAIM-AMOUNT FROM ARGUMENT-VALUE.
    DISPLAY 4 UPON ARGUMENT-NUMBER.
    ACCEPT WS-DAYS-ACTIVE FROM ARGUMENT-VALUE.

    IF WS-POLICY-ACTIVE NOT = "Y"
        STRING '{"status": "REJECTED", "message": "Policy is not active."}'
            DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO WS-OUTPUT
    ELSE
        IF WS-DAYS-ACTIVE < 30
            STRING '{"status": "REJECTED", "message": "Claims are not allowed within the first month of an active policy."}'
                DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO WS-OUTPUT
        ELSE
            IF WS-CLAIM-AMOUNT > WS-COVERAGE-REMAINING
                STRING '{"status": "REJECTED", "message": "Claim amount exceeds remaining coverage."}'
                    DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO WS-OUTPUT
            ELSE
                STRING '{"status": "APPROVED", "message": "Claim approved."}'
                    DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO WS-OUTPUT
            END-IF
        END-IF
    END-IF.

    DISPLAY FUNCTION TRIM(WS-OUTPUT).
    GOBACK.
